{"tid":1850130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠死都唔封關嘅陰謀？大家點睇","createTime":"2020-01-29T11:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T13:01:18.000Z","uid":250876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef15330c2e01862260a611976c0c1855cab070b1","tid":1850130,"uid":250876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"近排自從爆出武漢肺炎，少咗大量裸體浮屍同跳樓，林奠為咩死都唔肯封關，唔封關只會令到大量病源湧入香港，係香港社區爆發只會係必然嘅事實，而之前失蹤嘅手足如果已經走咗但未被處理，一旦香港社區爆發之後，呢啲手足好有可能會被染病！而當被標簽為病死嘅屍體必須盡快處理，極速火化，到時就可以名正言順大量處理屍體&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"916e6e053f23bd91b0b27421b912ed42d170f013","tid":1850130,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不封<br />\n攬炒</span>"},{"pid":"c5f3371e91a2612688a0b3c255e026c67393d93b","tid":1850130,"uid":250876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"916e6e053f23bd91b0b27421b912ed42d170f013","tid":1850130,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不封<br />\n攬炒</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:33:28.000Z","msg":"攬炒就一定㗎啦，但係都有個目的㗎？"},{"pid":"524afb6fc9f2f09a038c6dad2ceabcb582c01da3","tid":1850130,"uid":250876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:38:42.000Z","msg":"藍屍同中產都攬埋一份㗎喎，有錢佬都驚死㗎，佢再攪落去仲大鑊過沙士，社區爆發如果好似之前淘大咁，樓價跌，定係啲人諗住等樓價跌入貨？"},{"pid":"055226c955b22c08bc2d1df4e89f0ef28c9d1635","tid":1850130,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:57:19.000Z","msg":"市民：廢老太多，樓價太貴<br />\n林鄭：收到。會做野。"},{"pid":"3a31fb680c49c03fd2c5a7696d61d9dd60501879","tid":1850130,"uid":250876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"055226c955b22c08bc2d1df4e89f0ef28c9d1635","tid":1850130,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20